    <constraint source="CLAUDE.md §11">Component justification triple:
      1. Existing: PlaybookLibraryShell shared component already exists. Tasks 094 + 095 established the Dialog wrapper recipe + Path A.5 invocation pattern. Reuse both.
      2. Extension: this task adds affordance + Dialog wrapper at the third consumer surface. NO new shared component; NO duplicate Dialog wrapper logic (mirror tasks 094/095).
      3. Cost-of-doing-nothing: ad-hoc users cannot in-flow browse + invoke any playbook from the ad-hoc surface; FR-18 acceptance criterion (≥3 consumer surfaces) NOT met — this is the gating task.
    </constraint>
    <constraint source="fluent-v9-component skill">Apply Fluent UI v9 patterns + Spaarke conventions.</constraint>
